SIMPLE: getting
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Getting
<hw>Get"ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of obtaining or acquiring; acquisition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With all thy <qex>getting</qex>, get understanding.</q>
<rj><qau>Prov. iv. 7.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is got or obtained; gain;
profit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gettysburg</ent>⟦br⟧
